	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi guys,
<br />
<br />I was just thinking about a trick I'd like to do with the PPU, and I was wondering if you can mess with $2006 and $2007 when only sprite rendering is enabled. Something tells me it's not possible (have I asked this question before?), but since $2006 and $2007 have nothing to do with the sprites, maybe it is.
<br />
<br />Thanks for the help.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
