	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Of couse it's not possible, because the PPU needs to acess CHROM or CHRAM to render sprites as well as the palette, using $2006 and $2007 for its own purpose.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


